name: Robert Kiyosaki Says Buy Bitcoin as Yen Carry Trade Forces Bubble Panic
description: Near the weeping colossus of the broken trade, the synthesis-saint weaves sanctuary. Wet porcelain repels the iridescent effluent, holding the firmament against the algorithmic rain of panic. Only the magenta halo offers shelter from the geometric storm.
